sequenceDiagram
    participant API as API de ingestão
    participant PROD as Serviço de agendamento
    participant PAIQ as Fila pai
    participant PAIW as Worker pai
    participant FAN as Coordenador de fan-out
    participant FILAQ as Fila filha
    participant FILAW as Worker filho
    participant ING as IngestionService
    participant PDF as Pipeline PDF

    API->>PROD: prepara YAML e agenda o job pai
    PROD->>PAIQ: publica envelope prepared_yaml
    PAIQ->>PAIW: entrega job pai
    PAIW->>ING: execute_ingestion_async()
    ING->>FAN: decide entre sequencial e fan-out
    FAN->>FILAQ: publica document_fanout_child
    FILAQ->>FILAW: entrega documento filho
    FILAW->>ING: execute_single_document()
    ING->>PDF: processa o PDF do documento
